Text: Welcome to the MiniPlanThanks for registering a MiniPlan with Palo Alto Software Please use the following username to logon to The MiniPlan User name indexcfmaffiliatequicken The MiniPlan is in many ways a miniweb version of Business Plan Pro to give you a glimpse of what writing a full business plan will be like The MiniPlan is an excellent place to condense an idea If you are very serious about your business plan you should look at Business Plan Pro indexcfmfuseactionbusinessplanproaffiliatequicken Thanks Best of luck with the business Pat McCarthy Palo Alto Site Network
